title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Shea Serrano
description:
Welcome to the the debut of Throwing Fits: The Afters. This week we’re launching our weekly lightning round mini ep with Shea Serrano, and we're fucking around with The Ringer death match, partying with NBA legends, all time guilty pleasure zoovies, Lucha libre wrestling, and his last meal on earth.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
